        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="45" name="Message" rows="6" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
I just logged off and I have to say my intial impression is not a good one. To put it bluntly, we look like retards in skell form, our pets look like retards as well, In lich form with a pet up, its shameful looking. Our walk animation is a grotesque parody of what, I dont know. I cant post SS but what im talking about is better experienced than viewed anyhow.

Lich form is something im going to be embarrassed to use-I might even start accepting C2 rather than look like that, good grief. Our pets far from looking 'cool' 'fierce' or any other adjective you can think of, just stand there with a stupid hunch-backed slouch. Its hard to imagine a skell that manages to convey a look of stupidity and vacousness, but verant had succeeded!  The attack animations do not work atm, adding insult to injury, but I cant imagine that hunch backed moron looking anywhere near as good as my old monk did.

This is just my opinion, But I think weve been made to look like idiots. Not only nerfed to hell, but now we and our pets look like fools to boot. OTOH, those lieing whineing rangers new wolf forms look superb, obviously no expense was spared to make those lieing sniveling bastards look pretty. Our old (skell)forms may have been basic, plain even, but they did the job and looked 1/2 ways decent, these new ones, imo are a travesty.

56 Necro
Bertoxx

 
[/quote]</textarea><br>
        

